a:50:{i:1272469;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272469";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:254:"/me tensed up. An overwhelming sense of fear shot through him. This was it, it was all over, they were doomed. The inner foal in him was flailing its hooves frantically. &quot;Y-your Majesty.&quot; He said, removing his hat before entering the carriage. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424670207";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246702353";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272471;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272471";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:4:"text";s:480:"Princess_Celestia was sitting inside with the curtains pulled back on one side just enough so she could see the others at the station eating. She looked tranquil, as ever. &quot;Ah, Brake_Shoe, isn&#039;t it?&quot; she says, smiling as she turns to look at him. &quot;Please, won&#039;t you have a seat.&quot; She gestures to the seat across from her. The appointments were a little cramped...she was pretty large after all. &quot;I hope you have a moment to speak with me.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424670325";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246703230";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272479;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272479";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:271:"&quot;O-of course your Majesty.&quot; He said, as he made his way to the other side of the carriage. He carefully took a seat, holding his hat in his hooves. &quot;And y-yes, it&#039;s Brake Shoe...ma&#039;am.&quot; He&#039;d just knew, whatever it was, it would be bad. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424670443";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246704705";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272483;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272483";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:4:"text";s:131:"&quot;That was quite a ride we had coming down the mountain&quot; she says simply, still smiling, but now looking at him directly. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424670512";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246705100";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272490;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272490";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:187:"/me was sweating bullets. &quot;I-I do apologize for that your Majesty.&quot; They hadn&#039;t been the ones to lay the tracks, but they hadn&#039;t been around for the finalizing of it. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424670738";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246707664";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272494;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272494";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:4:"text";s:235:"&quot;Oh I don&#039;t think there&#039;s any need for apology&quot; she says politely. &quot;I was actually seeking some information from you...and your impressions on the ride so far. Has your engine met with your expectations?&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424670815";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246708126";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272498;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272498";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:254:"&quot;Expectation&#039;s ma&#039;am?&quot; He seemed confused. &quot;The engine has...survived-- Er, held up rather well. Still got the return journey, but that shouldn&#039;t be much of a problem. Tracks are straight from here back the Canterlot.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424671071";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246710987";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272504;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272504";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:4:"text";s:295:"&quot;I imagine, however, that you are looking for it to do something besides survive the trip, aren&#039;t you?&quot; she asks, still staring at him impassively. She hated it when ponies got nervous speaking to her, it made conversation difficult, but there wasn&#039;t any good way around it. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424671170";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246711677";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272509;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272509";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:216:"&quot;Well as...as we had explained to your Majesty previously. We were hoping to demonstrate how reliable transportation by rail would be. To expand...the project to other big cities.&quot; He twiddled with his hat.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424671275";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246713026";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272514;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272514";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:4:"text";s:317:"&quot;And do you think you&#039;re ready for that step right now?&quot; she asks, watching him fiddle with his hat. &quot;And please relax. As one responsible for all this, I am very interested in your opinion. Your HONEST opinion.&quot; She puts emphesis on that word, but she says it still in a very friendly tone. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424671574";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246715716";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272522;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272522";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:335:"/me stopped fiddling with his hat and took a deep breath. &quot;As it stands right now, the engine...could make the journey, but we&#039;d need to stop frequently for water and fuel.&quot; That was the honest truth. The Innovation was capable, but it wasn&#039;t that capable. From Canterlot to Manehattan would require several stops. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424671753";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246717805";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272525;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272525";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:4:"text";s:244:"/me nods. &quot;That was my impression too, based on what I&#039;ve seen. To be honest, I&#039;ve been gathering news about your experiment for some time now.&quot; She smiles a little bit at Brake_Shoe...perhaps it&#039;s a touch mischievious.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424671972";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246719702";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272527;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272527";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:189:"&quot;You, you have?&quot; He looked surprised. He didn&#039;t think their experiment all that important for the Princess herself to show any interest. This was an exciting turn of events. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424672224";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246722521";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272529;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272529";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:4:"text";s:138:"She nods. &quot;Tell me, besides the limitations of needing water and fuel, are there any other concerns you have over a much longer trip?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424672384";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246723823";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272531;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272531";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:279:"&quot;Well, as the trip up from Canterlot showed...we&#039;d need strong able ponies to lay the track and do it proper. A long distance trip be a feat, your Majesty, and it&#039;d take a long time to accomplish.&quot; He looked doubtful that such a thing would even be possible. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424672508";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246725346";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272532;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272532";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:4:"text";s:269:"&quot;Yes, of course...&quot; she replies, nodding quickly. &quot;But I am more interested in the technical aspects. Which specific problems need to be overcome. For instance, the pressure on the boiler over time, the reliability of the braking system and so on.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424672659";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246726566";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272536;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272536";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:237:"&quot;With time, I&#039;m sure we could develop better designs, your Majesty...but we&#039;d need funding to actually build the new designs. Everything would look well on pen and paper, but we&#039;d need to test these components.&quot; ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424672941";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246729686";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272548;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272548";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"63";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:4:"text";s:388:"For a few moments, Princess Celestia is silent...staring at Brake_Shoe, pondering. Finally she speaks again. &quot;Thank you for being candid with me&quot; she says, smiling. &quot;Now please, don&#039;t let me take up any more of your time. Get something to eat before we begin the return journey.&quot; Her long, elegant horn glows gracefully as she opens the door for Brake_Shoe again.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424673352";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#daea0f";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246733497";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#69d6ef";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1272551;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1272551";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Princess_Celestia";s:4:"text";s:261:"/me nodded politely and took up his hat and made his way out of the carriage. Once he was on solid ground, he made sure to bow to Princess Celestia before excusing himself. He had to go and tend to the engine now. Surely it was getting up quite a lot of steam. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424673550";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14246735783";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273249;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273249";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Flashpoint";s:4:"text";s:29:"Getting ready to start soon.~";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1424743831";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14247438603";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1273250;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1273250";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"8";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"45";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Brake_Shoe";s:1